Package com.example.n8tech.taskcan.Models

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Bid
    Bid represents a task provider that has made a bid on a task.
    BidList
    BidList contains an iterable ArrayList of Bid objects as well as methods that check for a specific bidder, return specific bidder indeces and the lowest bid on the list based on bid amount.
    CurrentUserSingleton
    CurrentUserSingleton represents the user of the app currently signed in.
    Task
    Task represents a task posted by a requester and stores task details.
    TaskList
    TaskList contains an iterable ArrayList of Task objects and related methods.
    User
    A User is a Task Requester and/or Task Provider.
    UserList
    UserList contains an iterable ArrayList of User objects and related methods.
